                        <p style="font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; margin:0 0 5px 0; padding:0; color:#000000; line-height:18px;">If you use a direct URL to link to Road to IELTS, this will change. When
            the switch is made, we will send an email confirming all the details.</p>				</td>
